Wildfire Data

Next Day Wildfire Spread

The Next Day Wildfire Spread dataset was developed by Google research as a benchmark largescale dataset for developing wildfire propagation machine learning models based on remote sensing data. The dataset contains 18454 fire samples in the contiguous United States from 2012 to 2020. The dataset includes the following features:
